Package: mekko
Type: Package
Title: Variable Width Charts: Marimekko and Bar Mekko
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Eric Rynerson <eric.rynerson@gmail.com> [aut, cre]",
    "Adam Evans <theadamevans@gmail.com> [ctb]"
  ))
Maintainer: Eric Rynerson <eric.rynerson@gmail.com>
Description: Create variable width bar and 100% stacked bar charts i.e.
    Marimekko and bar mekko charts to include important quantitative context.
    Synonymous with or closely related to mosaic, spine (or spinogram), matrix,
    submarine, olympic and Mondrian plots. Also, an alternative to tree maps.
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 0.4.3),
    ggplot2 (>= 2.0.0)
Suggests:
    tidyr(>= 0.4.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
